            <h3 class="fc-item__title fc-item__title--quoted"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2024/apr/28/some-are-born-lucky-so-the-left-shouldnt-flinch-from-giving-others-a-helping-hand" class="fc-item__link" data-link-name="article"> <span class="u-faux-block-link__cta fc-item__headline"> <span class="inline-garnett-quote inline-icon ">
                <svg width="70" height="49" viewbox="0 0 35 25" class="inline-garnett-quote__svg inline-icon__svg"><path d="M69.587.9c-1.842 15.556-3.89 31.316-4.708 48.1H37.043c3.07-16.784 8.391-32.544 17.602-48.1h14.942zM32.949.9c-2.047 15.556-4.094 31.316-4.912 48.1H.2C3.066 32.216 8.592 16.456 17.598.9h15.35z" />
                </svg> </span> <span class="js-headline-text">Some are born lucky, so the left shouldn’t flinch from giving others a helping hand</span> </span> </a></h3>
            <div class="fc-item__byline">
             Sonia Sodha
            </div>
           </div>
           <div class="fc-item__standfirst-wrapper fc-item__standfirst-wrapper--timestamp">
            <div class="fc-item__standfirst">
             When we mistakenly believe we live in a meritocracy, those in need are left behind
            </div>
